{"tid":151737,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東日本大震災6週年銀座YAHOO廣告","createTime":"2017-03-11T06:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T07:24:09.000Z","uid":3481,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"04f9baa413f3829982f83b4fec18838fd5f4573e","tid":151737,"uid":3481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T06:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C6nXnb-VwAA-YPj.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC6nXnb-VwAA-YPj.jpg%3Alarge&h=d91c6d5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每當３月１１日呢一日黎到，<br />\n我地就會回想起當時既情景。<br />\n東日本大震災距離依家已經<br />\n經過左６年。咩災害，唔會<br />\n再發生啦掛。每年我地都係<br />\n咁諗時，但災害大概，唔係，<br />\n一定會係某時候發生。果日，<br />\n係岩手縣大船渡市觀測得到<br />\n既海嘯，最高係１６.７m。如果<br />\n，呢個海嘯黎到銀座中心既話，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大約就係呢個高度。</strong></span></span><br />\n比想像仲要高出好多既感覺。<br />\n但係，單單只要知道呢個高度，<br />\n大家應該都會改變所採取既行動。<br />\n無錯，我地依家可以做既就係未<br />\n雨綢繆。係受災戶既記憶之中<br />\n能夠得到想像力，積存(防災既)智慧。<br />\n唔好唔記得果日。<br />\n呢樣，就係防災首應做既事 / 最好既防災*。<br />\n<br />\n*一番有第一樣 / 最好 既意思,個人覺得係度係偏向前者"},{"pid":"714e1ebf948d1755aac17bbf3c934ca2d2da8bff","tid":151737,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:10:24.000Z","msg":"今日大家幫手上日本Yahoo search  3 11<br />\nYahoo會捐10 yen 幫助災民 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家叫多啲朋友幫幫手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d1069e789fd67468c20e42038f8bb9f75c5a55","tid":151737,"uid":3481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s